snippet.title: CFB 25 Night Game GAMEPLAY! EA Sports College Football 25 Gameplay Pre snap penalty
snippet.description:
#newcollegefootballgame #easportscollegefootball #collegefootball25gameplay #CFB25 #NCAAFOOTBALL 


I found this video online and decided to add sound to the game! This happened in real life when Michigan traveled to PSU so i thought it would be cool to not only show pre play but add some mo bamba sound effects in there too which ultimately led to a michigan false start that night 

This is college football 25 pre snap gameplay at penn state at night. 

EA Sports college football 25 comes out on July 19th. 

WELCOME BACK!  Yesterday we got a gameplay deep dive video into the brand new EA Sports College football 25 game. The video had Kirk herbstriet narrating and talking about the Wear and tear system, Home environments and the new Passing system! Where you will need to rely on a passing meter like 2k to pass with accuracy. The home environments look insane with another loud / hype meter that will make your screen shake if you are the away team! This game is loaded with Abilities where you will be able to eqip up to 8 for your best players on your team.

This video showcases the field general ability that can be very effective when trying to figure out what the D is running . 

The offensive line logic looks to be VERY MUCH improved! Great double teams in the RPO game as well. 

This is college football 25 gameplay and the full game will be releasing on July 19th! Stay up to date with everything CFB 25 here on my channel as we get closer with more news coming soon about dynasty, rtg, ultimate team and more!

snippet.title: Donald Trump's brutal reaction to Joe Biden's disastrous day
snippet.description:
Former US President Donald Trump has brutally roasted US President Joe Biden following his disastrous press conference.

Within minutes of the oldest-ever sitting president’s presser, Biden called Vice President Kamala Harris, Donald Trump.

The embarrassing mistake happened very early on, with Trump posting to Truth Social about it shortly after.

“Crooked Joe begins his “Big Boy” Press Conference with, "I wouldn't have picked Vice President Trump to be vice president, though I think she was not qualified to be president." Great job, Joe!” wrote Trump.

Biden’s nearly hour-long presser allowed reporters to ask the president any un-scripted question.

The press conference followed Biden’s speech at the NATO summit in Washington.

snippet.title: 'The man needs help': Joe Biden fails NATO press conference
snippet.description:
Sky News host Gabriella Power said US President Joe Biden “needs help” after making several blunders at his “make or break” press conference. 

Hours before the press conference at the NATO Summit, Joe Biden accidentally referred to the leader of Ukraine as “President Putin”.  

Ms Power said it is “excruciatingly painful” watching Joe Biden become the “laughing stock of the world”. 

“The American people deserve better than this,” Ms Power said. 

“He has all the signs of a medical condition”.

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Jon Stewart on Biden 2024: It Is What It Is? | The Weekly Show With Jon Stewart
snippet.description:
After a lackluster debate performance, calls are mounting for President Biden to drop out of the 2024 race. Yet, he insists he is still running. Is this the right move? Joining us to explore our current conundrum, we’re joined by Jon Favreau and Tommy Vietor, Founders of Crooked Media, hosts of Pod Save America and Authors of "Democracy or Else: How to Save America in 10 Easy Steps," as well as Bakari Sellers, CNN political commentator and Author of "The Moment." Together, they hash out the best path forward for Democrats to defeat Trump this election and save democracy.
